OL,3,CMan who stabbed victim's skull in
OL,4,Cunprovoked nightclub attack jailed
OL,6,FA man who viciously attacked another
OL,7,Fman who was visiting the UK from
OL,8,FBarbados, leaving him for dead at a
OL,9,FReading nightclub, has been jailed for
OL,10,F27 years.
OL,12,FKrisma Anthony, 23, of Repository
OL,13,FRoad, Greenwich, London, was found
OL,14,Fguilty of attempted murder by a
OL,15,Fmajority verdict at Reading Crown
OL,16,FCourt on Wednesday 21 August.
OL,18,FAnthony had earlier pleaded guilty to
OL,19,Fpossession of a knife blade/sharp
OL,20,Fpointed object in a public place.
