OL,3,CMan who stabbed victim's skull in
OL,4,Cunprovoked nightclub attack jailed
OL,6,FJahlil Charles, aged 23, of no fixed
OL,7,Fabode, was acquitted of both charges.
OL,9,FAnthony had pleaded guilty to section
OL,10,F18 wounding with intent on day one of
OL,11,Fthe trial, but this plea was rejected
OL,12,Fby the prosecution.
OL,14,FTharel Thompson, 29, was visiting
OL,15,Ffamily in the UK from the Caribbean
OL,16,Fwhen he was attacked in the toilet
OL,17,Fcorridor of the Walkabout Bar in
OL,18,FWiston Terrace, Reading, in the early
OL,19,Fhours of Sunday 11 February.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/8
