OL,3,CMan who stabbed victim's skull in
OL,4,Cunprovoked nightclub attack jailed
OL,6,FMr Thompson was stabbed in the head
OL,7,Fand sustained life-changing injuries.
OL,9,FCCTV captured Mr Thompson leaving the
OL,10,Ftoilet at just before 2am. He appears
OL,11,Fto fist-pump Charles, and there did
OL,12,Fnot appear to be any animosity.
OL,14,FHowever, minutes later, Anthony
OL,15,Fstabbed Mr Thompson through his skull
OL,16,Fin an unprovoked attack, leaving him
OL,17,Flying in the corridor critically
OL,18,Finjured.
OL,20,FAnthony was arrested later that day
OL,21,Fand was charged on 13 February.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/8
