OL,4,Cunprovoked nightclub attack jailed
OL,6,FCharles was arrested on 23 February
OL,7,Fand charged on 25 February.
OL,9,FSenior investigating officer Detective
OL,10,FInspector Nick Hind, of the Major
OL,11,FCrime Unit, said: "Whatever the cause
OL,12,Fof disagreement between Mr Thompson
OL,13,Fand Anthony, there can be no doubt
OL,14,Fthat this was a vicious, needless and
OL,15,Fapparently unprovoked attack.
OL,17,F"He left Mr Thompson for dead in the
OL,18,Fcorridor of the nightclub before
OL,19,Fmaking good his escape.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/8
