OL,3,CMan who stabbed victim's skull in
OL,4,Cunprovoked nightclub attack jailed
OL,6,F"Mr Thompson sustained very severe
OL,7,Finjuries, and it is nothing short of a
OL,8,Fmiracle that he did not die as a
OL,9,Fresult of this attack.
OL,11,F"I would like to pay tribute to the
OL,12,Fexpertise of the surgeons who operated
OL,13,Fon Mr Thompson and the nurses and
OL,14,Fother medical professionals that
OL,15,Fprovided incredible care for him.
OL,17,F"However, despite this, the impacts
OL,18,Fthat this attack has had on Mr
OL,19,FThompson are life changing in the
OL,20,Fextreme.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/8
