OL,4,Cunprovoked nightclub attack jailed
OL,6,F"At the conclusion of this trial, I
OL,7,Fwould also like to pay tribute to Mr
OL,8,FThompson's family and to Mr Thompson
OL,9,Fhimself.
OL,11,F"Not only have they had to endure a
OL,12,Flong and harrowing investigation, but
OL,13,Fhave suffered financially as well as
OL,14,Fthey have needed to find the funds to
OL,15,Fensure Mr Thompson got the medical
OL,16,Ftreatment that he needed.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/8
