OL,3,CMan who stabbed victim's skull in
OL,4,Cunprovoked nightclub attack jailed
OL,6,F"No family should have to endure this,
OL,7,Fand it is testament to them that they
OL,8,Fhave supported this investigation
OL,9,Fthrough to what I hope they feel is a
OL,10,Fsatisfactory conclusion for them.
OL,12,F"I would like to wish Mr Thompson and
OL,13,Fhis family all good wishes for the
OL,14,Ffuture, which they will have to live
OL,15,Fwith coping with the significant
OL,16,Fimplications from this horrific
OL,17,Fincident."
